### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AI-MSHM  –  Settings Endpoints
###  Base prefix: /api/v1/settings/
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl      = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType  = application/json
@accessToken  = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  NOTIFICATION PREFERENCES
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### GET current notification preferences
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/notifications/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### UPDATE notification preferences (partial – send only what changed)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/notifications/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "morning_time": "07:30",
  "evening_time": "20:00",
  "morning_checkin_enabled": true,
  "evening_checkin_enabled": true,
  "weekly_prompts_enabled": true,
  "period_alerts_enabled": true,
  "risk_score_updates_enabled": true,
  "wearable_sync_reminders": false,
  "do_not_disturb": false
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TURN ON do-not-disturb only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/notifications/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "do_not_disturb": true
}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  CONNECTED DEVICES
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### LIST connected devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CONNECT Apple Watch
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "device_type": "apple_watch",
  "device_name": "Apple Watch Series 9",
  "sync_frequency": "15min",
  "background_sync": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CONNECT Fitbit
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "device_type": "fitbit",
  "device_name": "Fitbit Sense 2",
  "sync_frequency": "30min",
  "background_sync": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CONNECT Garmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "device_type": "garmin",
  "device_name": "Garmin Forerunner 955",
  "sync_frequency": "1h",
  "background_sync": false
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CONNECT Oura Ring
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "device_type": "oura_ring",
  "device_name": "Oura Ring Gen 3",
  "sync_frequency": "1h",
  "background_sync": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### GET single device  (replace 1 with real id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### UPDATE device sync settings
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "sync_frequency": "5min",
  "background_sync": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TRIGGER MANUAL SYNC
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/1/sync/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### DISCONNECT a device
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/settings/devices/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  PRIVACY SETTINGS
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### GET privacy settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/privacy/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### UPDATE privacy & consent settings (partial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/privacy/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "behavioral_data_enabled": true,
  "wearable_data_enabled": true,
  "clinical_data_enabled": true,
  "share_with_clinician": true,
  "anonymized_research": false,
  "model_improvement": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### TOGGLE research consent only
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/settings/privacy/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "anonymized_research": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### REQUEST DATA EXPORT  (queues email with download link)
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/privacy/export/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### DELETE ACCOUNT  ⚠️  IRREVERSIBLE
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/settings/privacy/delete-account/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
